[[File:University of Mississippi Innovation Hub at Insight Park.jpg|thumb|right|The Innovation Hub at Insight Park in 2018.]] The '''Insight Park''' at the [[University of Mississippi]] is a [[business park]] next to Ole Miss's campus in [[Oxford, Mississippi]]. Construction began in 2010,<ref name="clarionledgerunderway">{{cite news |title=Ole Miss: Research park work under way |url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/185584978/?terms=%22insight%2Bpark%22 |accessdate=July 29, 2018 |work=The Clarion-Ledger |location=Jackson, Mississippi |date=June 12, 2010|page=15|via=[[Newspapers.com]]|registration=yes}}</ref> and the park was dedicated in 2012.<ref name="clarionledgerfacilityopens">{{cite news |title=Research facility opens |url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/186041207/?terms=%22insight%2Bpark%22 |accessdate=July 29, 2018 |work=The Clarion-Ledger |location=Jackson, Mississippi |date=April 15, 2012|page=20|via=[[Newspapers.com]]|registration=yes}}</ref>
[[Eldon Insurance]] and Big Data Pharma, two companies owned by British businessman [[Arron Banks]], signed a lease in Insight Park in February 2018 on the recommendation of Mississippi Governor [[Phil Bryant]].<ref name="clarionledgerbryanthadrole">{{cite news |last1=Harris |first1=Bracey |title=Bryant had role in Ole Miss's tie to firm. Britons allegedly used contentious data mining. |url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/420168176 |accessdate=July 29, 2018 |work=The Clarion-Ledger|location=Jackson, Mississippi |date=April 20, 2018|pages=A1; A7|via=[[Newspapers.com]]|registration=yes}}</ref> As of June 2018, a $200,000 office building is expected to be built for Big Data Pharma, potentially paid for by the [[Mississippi Development Authority]] and the University of Mississippi Research Foundation, for an annual lease of $78,000.<ref name="jacksonfreepressupdatedinside">{{cite news |last1=Dreher |first1=Arielle |title=UPDATED: Inside the ‘Brexit Boys’ Data Project at Ole Miss |url=http://www.jacksonfreepress.com/news/2018/jun/07/brexit-boys-data-project-ole-miss-could-use-missis/ |accessdate=July 29, 2018 |work=Jackson Free Press |date=June 7, 2018}}</ref>
