This is a '''list of supermarket chains in [[Algeria]]'''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://yellowpages.cybo.com/algeria-area_code/5/grocery-stores-and-supermarkets/|title=Grocery Stores And Supermarkets In Algeria|date=|accessdate=10 October 2014| publisher=Algeria Yellow Pages - Cybo}}</ref>
The Algerian chain Ardis (owned by Algerian group [[Arcofina]]) is currently operating one hypermarket in the country in [[Mohammedia, Algiers|Mohammedia]] just outside [[Algiers]]. In the future Ardis will open 19 hypermarkets in the country, the next hypermarket will open near [[Oran]] in [[Bir El Djir]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.algerie-focus.com/blog/2012/07/06/lhypermarche-ardis-a-ouvert-ses-portes-a-alger/|title=L'hypermarché Ardis a ouvert ses portes à Alger - Algérie Focus|date=6 July 2012|publisher=|accessdate=8 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.algerie360.com/algerie/lhypermarche-ardis-ouvre-ses-portes-demain-au-grand-public/|title=L’hypermarché Ardis ouvre ses portes demain au grand public - Algérie360|date=3 July 2012|publisher=|accessdate=8 April 2017}}</ref> [[Carrefour]] ended their partnership with the Algerian group Arcofina in February 19, 2009. "The concept of mass distribution does not work in Algeria," added Carrefour. Before that, Carrefour had still only one store opened as of 2009, of 18 hypermarkets planned by 2012. The private group Arcofina explained that there was a delay because of difficulties in finding available land for hypermarkets. Arcofina is now focusing on opening hypermarkets in the future under the Ardis brand.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.regoverningmarkets.org/en/news/global/carrefour_exits_algeria.html|title=Regoverningmarkets.org - My Diary Blog|publisher=|accessdate=8 April 2017|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130415164813/http://www.regoverningmarkets.org/en/news/global/carrefour_exits_algeria.html|archivedate=15 April 2013|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://lexpansion.lexpress.fr/entreprise/carrefour-quitte-le-marche-algerien-sur-un-echec_175017.html|title=Entreprises - Economie d'entreprise|publisher=|accessdate=8 April 2017}}</ref>
